detailedReviews.text: Liv Pure A√ßa√≠ catered my daughter‚Äôs wedding reception. We appreciated having a unique, refreshing, and healthy option for our guests. When considering allergy and digestive intolerance issues for some of them, it was important to have inclusive food. The a√ßa√≠ also told a story about our daughter‚Äôs life. It was perfect and delicious.

Something I need to point out tho for everyone & also the company‚Ä¶. They need to be careful of allergen cross contamination. The smoothie we got, island smoothie does not have nuts in it. My son has a nut allergy and after drinking his smoothie couldn‚Äôt stop coughing and his chin area around his face was red. Luckily for us, minor cross contamination is ok but there are others out there who are not ok with cross contamination so I‚Äôd recommend the company to just figure out a way to keep all allergens separate. Not sure how as im not in the food business but this is important.
